      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIESTA (10) returned in fine fashion with a solid win at Eagle Farm when having her first run for the new yard and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Winning hoop Graham sticks in the saddle and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Should prove very tough to hold out again. EXTREME DIAMOND (5) just found one better here when resuming and will strip fitter with that run now in the locker. Include from the low draw. WINCHMAN (4) is a very consistent conveyance who doesn't know how to run a bad race. Has a win and a second from three spins around this circuit and has to be included in calculations. RUINS OF ROME (3) boasts a win over this course and distance and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Capable of sharp improvement on that first-up effort. NO NAME FRANK (6) next in line.",
